{
  "texts": [
    "Program repair requires a large number of time costs and human resources from the project development team [538].",
    "Due to the growing demand for efficient software maintenance, automatic program repair techniques have emerged as a solution [539].Automatic program repair allows developers to automate (or nearly automate) defect detection and correction.",
    "This makes program repair efficient, reliable, and cost-effective [540].",
    "In recent years, the development and implementation of automatic program repair techniques have been widely recognized by the software development community [541].",
    "The success of deep learning in recent years makes it a promising approach for locating and repairing buggy programs."
  ]
}